<normalizedToken id="C0C951839AC22691B50AA9DE1686BC1E" originalValue="Maranhão">Maranhao</normalizedToken>
, Minas Gerais, Rio de Janeiro, 
<normalizedToken id="EAA4DD457EF118A0A92E0176C876DF33" originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Paulo and now in 
<normalizedToken id="F6964210712D19496D99F52B6C79C0E7" originalValue="Rondônia">Rondonia</normalizedToken>
) and Paraguay (
<bibRefCitation id="2A3D5656F7C730926E38B07623F4DC26" author="Borkent, A." editor="Adis, J." journalOrPublisher="Pensoft, Sofia-Moscow" pageId="0" pageNumber="13075" title="Aquatic Biodiversity in Latin America (ABLA)" year="2007">Borkent and Spinelli 2007</bibRefCitation>
