<bibRefCitation id="274AF3505A6522D52B5A849C3D8C86FD" author="Farias, Emanuelle Sousa" journalOrPublisher="Check List" pageId="0" pageNumber="13075" pagination=": 2002" title="List of Culicoides biting midges (Diptera: Ceratopogonidae) from the state of Amazonas, Brazil, including new records" volume="12" year="2016">Farias et al. 2016a</bibRefCitation>
